  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Create your own animal character, or even a monstrosity!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/af3008ab2601b5be96e138fd1f45cfc5.poster.avif?t=1773682812\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/af3008ab2601b5be96e138fd1f45cfc5.webm?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/af3008ab2601b5be96e138fd1f45cfc5.mp4?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">In this creative sandbox, hundreds of options are at your fingertips to make your own characters, or recreate something familiar!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/85e4188c6fb3fc78bd653c5ac912dd28.poster.avif?t=1773682812\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/85e4188c6fb3fc78bd653c5ac912dd28.webm?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/85e4188c6fb3fc78bd653c5ac912dd28.mp4?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Make a little creature, and fling them around. Watch them run, interact with each other, and play. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Create A Huge Variety Of Characters!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/8308e5d0df0b3adbbfde4a6108df9d94.poster.avif?t=1773682812\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/8308e5d0df0b3adbbfde4a6108df9d94.webm?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/8308e5d0df0b3adbbfde4a6108df9d94.mp4?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Quadspillions of Combinations!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/9467521484924cf38d1f1d0873448f8f.poster.avif?t=1773682812\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/9467521484924cf38d1f1d0873448f8f.webm?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/9467521484924cf38d1f1d0873448f8f.mp4?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Use them as Vtubers, with mic detection for mouth flaps! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/082f84de1e97b4d263a4436b84eed8ed.poster.avif?t=1773682812\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/082f84de1e97b4d263a4436b84eed8ed.webm?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/082f84de1e97b4d263a4436b84eed8ed.mp4?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><br></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Create your own animal character, or even a monstrosity!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/af3008ab2601b5be96e138fd1f45cfc5.poster.avif?t=1773682812\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/af3008ab2601b5be96e138fd1f45cfc5.webm?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/af3008ab2601b5be96e138fd1f45cfc5.mp4?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">In this creative sandbox, hundreds of options are at your fingertips to make your own characters, or recreate something familiar!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/85e4188c6fb3fc78bd653c5ac912dd28.poster.avif?t=1773682812\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/85e4188c6fb3fc78bd653c5ac912dd28.webm?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/85e4188c6fb3fc78bd653c5ac912dd28.mp4?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Make a little creature, and fling them around. Watch them run, interact with each other, and play. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Create A Huge Variety Of Characters!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/8308e5d0df0b3adbbfde4a6108df9d94.poster.avif?t=1773682812\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/8308e5d0df0b3adbbfde4a6108df9d94.webm?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/8308e5d0df0b3adbbfde4a6108df9d94.mp4?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Quadspillions of Combinations!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/9467521484924cf38d1f1d0873448f8f.poster.avif?t=1773682812\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/9467521484924cf38d1f1d0873448f8f.webm?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/9467521484924cf38d1f1d0873448f8f.mp4?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Use them as Vtubers, with mic detection for mouth flaps! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/082f84de1e97b4d263a4436b84eed8ed.poster.avif?t=1773682812\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/082f84de1e97b4d263a4436b84eed8ed.webm?t=1773682812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295120/extras/082f84de1e