      "voted_up": true,
      "votes_up": 1,
      "playtime_at_review": 190,
      "review_text": "FIRE!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! lots of customization, very silly creatures",
      "timestamp_created": 1774042831
    },
    {
      "review_id": "221212132",
      "author_steamid": "76561199232972103",
      "voted_up": true,
      "votes_up": 1,
      "playtime_at_review": 119,
      "review_text": "(My playtime is longer than it seems, since I bought the game on Itch.io and also played a fair bit of its free version.)\n\nA fun little Mii-Maker styled character creator, but that's all it is. Once you make your creatures, all you can do is watch them wander around and talk to each other, or pick them up and shake them around if you're feeling fancy. Your mileage will vary [i]strongly[/i] here.\n\nDo you want a nifty little tool to make or recreate OCs with? The ability to make a dinky V-tuber model, perhaps? Great, then you will like this! But if you were hoping to be able to [i]do[/i] things with your little guys, look elsewhere.",
      "timestamp_created": 1774050629
    }
  ]
